<!--pages/bind/bind.wxml-->
<view class="container">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">我的邀请码</view>
    <view class="my-code">{{myCode || '------'}}</view>
    <button class="btn-primary" bindtap="copyCode">复制邀请码</button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">输入对方邀请码</view>
    <input
      class="code-input"
      placeholder="请输入 6 位邀请码"
      value="{{inputCode}}"
      bindinput="onCodeInput"
      maxlength="10"
    />
    <button class="btn-primary" bindtap="doBind">确认绑定</button>
  </view>

  <view class="tip text-muted">
    绑定后双方的积分将互相可见，绑定关系一旦建立不能随意解除。
  </view>
</view>
